Th vin pandas

by Maxwell Margenot

Edited by AI Cafe

Pandas l mt th vin Python cung cp mt tp hp cc cu trc d liu mnh m gip bn qun l d liu tt hn. Trong bi ging ny, chng ta s cp n cch s dng cc i tng Series v DataFrame x l d liu. Nhng i tng ny c s tch hp mnh m vi NumPy, cho php chng ta d dng thc hin cc php tnh thng k v ton hc cn thit cho lnh vc ti chnh.

In[1]:
import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

Vi pandas, vic lu tr, trc quan ha v thc hin cc php tnh trn d liu ca bn tr nn d dng. Ch vi vi dng m, chng ta c th chnh sa d liu v trnh by n theo cch d hiu. y, chng ta m phng mt s t sut sinh li trong NumPy, a chng vo mt DataFrame ca pandas v thc hin cc php tnh chuyn chng thnh gi c v v th, tt c ch vi vi dng m.

In[2]:
returns = pd.DataFrame(np.random.normal(1.0, 0.03, (100, 10)))
prices = returns.cumprod()
prices.plot()
plt.title('Randomly-generated Prices')
plt.xlabel('Time')
plt.ylabel('Price')
plt.legend(loc=0);

Vy hy cng xem xt cch chng ta i tng bc n im ny nh!

Cu trc d liu trong pandas

Series

Mt Series trong pandas l mt mng 1 chiu vi cc nhn c th cha bt k loi d liu no. Chng c s dng ch yu x l d liu chui thi gian. Vic to mt Series rt n gin, ch cn gi pandas.Series() trn mt danh sch Python hoc mng NumPy.

In[3]:
s = pd.Series([1, 2, np.nan, 4, 5])
print(s)

0    1.0
1    2.0
2    NaN
3    4.0
4    5.0
dtype: float64

Mi Series u c mt tn. Chng ta c th t tn cho chui d liu ny qua tham s hoc c th nh ngha sau bng cch truy cp trc tip vo thuc tnh tn. Trong trng hp ny, chng ta khng t tn cho chui thi gian ca mnh, v vy thuc tnh ny s trng.

In[4]:
print(s.name)

None

Tn ny c th c sa i trc tip m khng gy hu qu g.

In[5]:
s.name = "Toy Series"
print(s.name)

Toy Series

Chng ta gi cc nhn trc c thu thp ca mt Series l ch mc ca n. Mt ch mc c th c truyn vo mt Series nh mt tham s hoc c thm vo sau, tng t nh tn ca n. Trong trng hp khng c ch mc, mt Series s n gin cha mt ch mc c to thnh t cc s nguyn, bt u t $0$, nh trong trng hp ca "Toy Series" ca chng ta.

In[6]:
print(s.index)

RangeIndex(start=0, stop=5, step=1)

Pandas c mt hm tch hp sn c bit to ch s ngy, l date_range(). Chng ta s dng hm ny to mt ch s mi cho s.

In[7]:
new_index = pd.date_range("2025-01-01", periods=len(s), freq="D")
print(new_index)

DatetimeIndex(['2025-01-01', '2025-01-02', '2025-01-03', '2025-01-04',
               '2025-01-05'],
              dtype='datetime64[ns]', freq='D')

Ch mc phi c di chnh xc bng vi Series . Mi ch mc phi khp mt-mt vi tng phn t ca Series. Khi iu ny c tha mn, chng ta c th trc tip sa i ch mc ca Series, ging nh vi tn, s dng ch mc mi mang nhiu thng tin hn (mt cch tng i).

In[8]:
s.index = new_index
print(s.index)

DatetimeIndex(['2025-01-01', '2025-01-02', '2025-01-03', '2025-01-04',
               '2025-01-05'],
              dtype='datetime64[ns]', freq='D')

Ch s ca Series rt quan trng trong vic x l chui thi gian, iu ny chng ta s tm hiu k hn phn sau.

Truy cp cc phn t ca Series

Series thng c truy cp bng cch s dng cc phng thc iloc[] v loc[]. Chng ta s dng iloc[] truy cp cc phn t theo ch s nguyn v s dng loc[] truy cp theo ch s ca Series.

In[9]:
print("First element of the series:", s.iloc[0])
print("Last element of the series:", s.iloc[len(s)-1])

First element of the series: 1.0
Last element of the series: 5.0

Chng ta c th ct (slice) mt Series tng t nh collections, Python lists v NumPy arrays. Chng ta s dng ton t hai chm ch nh phn ct.

In[10]:
s.iloc[:2]
Out[10]:
Toy Series
2025-01-01 1.0
2025-01-02 2.0

Khi to mt on ct, chng ta c cc ty chn ch nh mt im bt u, mt im kt thc v mt bc nhy. on ct s bt u t ch s bt u v ly cc bc c kch thc step cho n khi vt qua ch s kt thc, khng bao gm ch s kt thc.

In[11]:
start = 0
end = len(s) - 1
step = 1

s.iloc[start:end:step]
Out[11]:
Toy Series
2025-01-01 1.0
2025-01-02 2.0
2025-01-03 NaN
2025-01-04 4.0

Chng ta thm ch c th o ngc mt Series bng cch ch nh kch thc bc m.

In[12]:
s.iloc[::-1]
Out[12]:
Toy Series
2025-01-05 5.0
2025-01-04 4.0
2025-01-03 NaN
2025-01-02 2.0
2025-01-01 1.0

Tng t, chng ta c th ch mc cho im bt u v kt thc bng mt gi tr nguyn m.

In[13]:
s.iloc[-2:-4:-1]
Out[13]:
Toy Series
2025-01-04 4.0
2025-01-03 NaN

Chng ta cng c th truy cp mt chui bng cch s dng cc gi tr ca ch s ca n. V chng ta lp ch mc cho s bng mt tp hp cc ngy thng (cc i tng Timestamp), nn chng ta c th xem gi tr cha trong s cho mt ngy c th.

In[14]:
s.loc['2025-01-01']
Out[14]:
np.float64(1.0)

Hoc thm ch cho mt khong thi gian c th!

In[15]:
s.loc['2025-01-02':'2025-01-04']
Out[15]:
Toy Series
2025-01-02 2.0
2025-01-03 NaN
2025-01-04 4.0

Vi Series, chng ta c th ch s dng du ngoc vung ([]) truy cp cc phn t, nhng y khng phi l cch vit tt nht. Du ngoc vung c th gy nhm ln v chng c th c s dng truy cp Series (v DataFrames) bng c gi tr ch s v gi tr s nguyn, v kt qu s thay i da trn ng cnh (c bit l vi DataFrames).

Lp ch mc Boolean

Ngoi cc phng php truy cp cp trn, bn c th lc Series bng cch s dng cc mng boolean. Series tng thch vi cc ton t so snh tiu chun ca bn. Khi c so snh vi bt k iu kin no m bn thch, bn s nhn c mt Series khc, ln ny c lp y bng cc gi tr boolean.

In[16]:
print(s < 3)

2025-01-01     True
2025-01-02     True
2025-01-03    False
2025-01-04    False
2025-01-05    False
Freq: D, Name: Toy Series, dtype: bool

Chng ta c th a li chui Series ny vo chui Series gc lc ra ch nhng phn t m iu kin ca chng l True.

In[17]:
print(s.loc[s < 3])

2025-01-01    1.0
2025-01-02    2.0
Freq: D, Name: Toy Series, dtype: float64

Nu mun, chng ta c th nhm nhiu iu kin li vi nhau bng cch s dng cc ton t logic &, |, v ~ (v, hoc, v khng, tng ng).

In[18]:
print(s.loc[(s < 3) & (s > 1)])

2025-01-02    2.0
Freq: D, Name: Toy Series, dtype: float64

iu ny rt tin li ly ch nhng phn t ca mt Series p ng cc tiu ch c th m chng ta cn. N tr nn thun tin hn khi chng ta lm vic vi DataFrames.

Lp ch mc v D liu chui thi gian (Time Series)

V chng ta s dng Series x l d liu chui thi gian, nn vic tm hiu mt cht v cch chng ta x l thnh phn thi gian l iu ng lu tm. i vi mc ch ca chng ta, chng ta s dng cc i tng Timestamp ca pandas. Hy ly mt chui thi gian y , hon chnh vi tt c cc nhn ph hp, bng cch s dng hm get_prices(). Tt c d liu c ly vi get_prices() s nh dng DataFrame. Chng ta c th sa i ch mc ny theo cch m chng ta mun.

Lu rng DatetimeIndex ny c mt tp hp thng tin lin quan. C th, n c mt tn sut lin quan (freq) v mt mi gi lin quan (tz). Tn sut cho bit d liu l hng ngy, hng thng hay mt khong thi gian khc, trong khi mi gi cho bit ch s ny tng i vi a phng no. Chng ta c th iu chnh tt c thng tin b sung ny!

Nu chng ta ly mu li Series, chng ta c th iu chnh tn sut ca d liu. Hin ti, chng ta c d liu hng ngy (khng bao gm cui tun). Hy gim xung t d liu hng ngy ny xung d liu hng thng bng cch s dng phng thc resample().

In[32]:
def custom_resampler(array_like):
    """ Returns the first value of the period """
    return array_like.iloc[0]

first_of_month_prices = prices.resample('ME').apply(custom_resampler)

Ngoi kh nng qun l mi gi v tn sut, mi chui thi gian u c phng thc reindex() c tch hp sn m chng ta c th s dng iu chnh li d liu hin c theo mt tp hp nhn ch mc mi. Nu d liu khng tn ti cho mt nhn c th, d liu s c in bng mt gi tr gi ch. Thng thng l np.nan, mc d chng ta c th cung cp mt phng thc in gi tr ny.

Bn s nhn thy rng chng ta vn c mt vi gi tr NaN ngay u chui thi gian ca chng ta. iu ny l do ngy 1 thng 1 nm 2021 l mt ngy l, theo sau l nhng ngy ngh cui tun! Bi v y l nhng im d liu sm nht v chng ta khng c thng tin no t trc , nn chng khng th c in gi tr pha trc. Chng ta s x l nhng gi tr NaN ny trong phn tip theo, khi chng ta gii quyt vn d liu b thiu.

D liu b thiu

Khi chng ta x l d liu thc, c kh nng rt thc t l gp phi cc gi tr b thiu. D liu thc thng c nhiu l hng v pandas cung cp cho chng ta nhng cch x l chng. i khi, vic ly mu li hoc thay i ch mc c th to ra cc gi tr NaN. May mn thay, pandas cung cp cho chng ta cc phng php x l chng. Chng ta c hai phng php chnh i ph vi d liu b thiu. Phng php u tin l in vo d liu b thiu bng hm fillna(). V d, gi s rng chng ta mun in vo cc ngy b thiu vi gi trung bnh ca tt c cc ngy.

S dng fillna() th kh d dng. Ch cn ch nh gi tr m bn mun in vo cc khong trng. Tuy nhin, trng hp ny khng thc s hp l, v nhng l do c tho lun trong bi ging v tnh dng trong chui bi ging. Chng ta c th in chng bng $0$, nhng iu cng khng cung cp thng tin hu ch.

Thay v in cc gi tr c th bng fillna(), chng ta c th s dng phng thc bfill() "in li", ni m cc gi tr NaN s c in bng gi tr c in tip theo (thay v gi tr c in cui cng trong phng php in tin).

Nhng mt ln na, y l mt tng ti v nhng l do ging nh ty chn trc. C hai gii php c gi l ny u tnh n d liu tng lai m khng c sn ti thi im cc im d liu m chng ta ang c gng lp y. Trong trng hp s dng trung bnh hoc trung v, cc thng k tm tt ny c tnh ton bng cch xem xt ton b chui thi gian. Vic in li ging nh ni rng gi ca mt chng khon c th hm nay, ngay by gi, l gi ca ngy mai. iu ny cng khng hp l. C hai ty chn ny u l v d v thin lch nhn trc (look-ahead bias), s dng d liu s khng c bit hoc khng c sn vo thi im mong mun, chng ta nn trnh s dng nh vy.

Ty chn tip theo ca chng ta hp dn hn nhiu. Chng ta c th n gin loi b d liu b thiu bng phng php dropna(). y l mt la chn tt hn nhiu so vi vic in cc gi tr NaN bng cc s ty .

Nhiu hm NumPy s hot ng trn Series tng t nh cch chng hot ng trn cc mng NumPy 1 chiu.

In[51]:
print(np.median(mult_returns))

0.0009848297169151587

Hu ht cc chc nng ny, tuy nhin, c trin khai trc tip di dng cc phng thc ca Series v DataFrame.

In[52]:
print(mult_returns.median())

0.0009848297169151587

Trong mi trng hp, vic s dng phng thc tch hp sn ca pandas s tt hn so vi vic s dng hm NumPy trn mt cu trc d liu pandas do nhng ci tin v hiu sut. Hy chc chn kim tra ti liu v Series trc khi tm n cc php tnh khc cho cc hm thng thng.

DataFrames

Nhiu kha cnh trong vic lm vic vi Series cng p dng cho DataFrames. DataFrames trong pandas cho php chng ta d dng qun l d liu ca mnh vi cu trc trc quan.

Ging nh Series, DataFrames c th cha nhiu loi d liu khc nhau, nhng DataFrames l i tng 2 chiu, khng ging nh Series. Mi DataFrame c mt thuc tnh ch mc (index) v thuc tnh ct (columns), m chng ta s cp chi tit hn khi bt u thc s lm vic vi mt i tng. Thuc tnh ch mc ging nh ch mc ca mt Series, mc d ch mc trong pandas c mt s tnh nng b sung m chng ti rt tic l khng th cp y. Nu bn quan tm n iu ny, hy xem ti liu pandas v lp ch mc nng cao. Thuc tnh ct cung cp chiu th hai cho cc DataFrame, cho php chng ta kt hp cc ct t tn (tt c l Series), thnh mt i tng ng nht vi ch mc c cn chnh.

Chng ta c th to mt DataFrame bng cch gi pandas.DataFrame() trn mt t in hoc mng NumPy (ndarray). Chng ta cng c th ni mt nhm cc Series ca pandas thnh mt DataFrame bng cch s dng pandas.concat().

In[53]:
dict_data = {
    'a' : [1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
    'b' : ['L', 'K', 'J', 'M', 'Z'],
    'c' : np.random.normal(0, 1, 5)
}
print(dict_data)

{'a': [1, 2, 3, 4, 5], 'b': ['L', 'K', 'J', 'M', 'Z'], 'c': array([0.30945519, 0.17517803, 0.45152922, 0.42528089, 0.28562943])}

Mi DataFrame c mt s thuc tnh quan trng m chng ta cn ghi nh. Thuc tnh u tin trong s ny l thuc tnh ch mc. Chng ta c th d dng bao gm mt ch mc ca cc i tng Timestamp ging nh chng ta lm vi Series.

Nh cp trn, chng ta c th kt hp Series thnh DataFrames. Vic ni Series nh th ny s ghp cc phn t da trn ch s tng ng ca chng. V cc Series di y khng c ch s c gn, nn chng mi ci s mc nh s dng ch s s nguyn.

In[55]:

Mi DataFrame cng c thuc tnh columns. Nhng thuc tnh ny c th c gn khi chng ta gi pandas.DataFrame hoc c th c sa i trc tip ging nh ch s. Lu rng khi chng ta ni hai Series trn, tn ct l tn ca nhng Series .

Phn tch chui thi gian vi pandas

S dng cc phng php thng k tch hp sn cho DataFrames, chng ta c th thc hin cc php tnh trn nhiu chui thi gian cng mt lc! M thc hin cc php tnh trn DataFrames y gn nh hon ton ging vi cc phng php c s dng cho Series trn, v vy ng lo lng v vic phi hc li mi th.

Phng thc plot() li xut hin y, ln ny vi mt ch thch tch hp sn tng ng vi tn ca cc ct m bn ang v.
